"score\": 0.9999999998835847, \"rank\": 1.155149782990459e-10, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 2024 Paris Olympics has gone full Woke dystopian.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.150499354611594e-42, \"text\": \"Woke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony was filled with transgend*r mockery of the Last Supper, the Golden Calf idol, and even the Pale Horse from the Book of Revelation.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics has made it clear that Christian viewers are not welcome,\\\" Texas-based journalist Kyle Becker wrote on his social media handle on 'X'.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999129373016725, \"rank\": 8.707027881357418e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"score\": 0.9999970541064349, \"rank\": 2.9459024103948432e-06, \"text\": \"Kyle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Broflovski\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", \"score\": 0.9999616143928152, \"rank\": 1.5927601021183758e-05, \"text\": \"Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boris_Becker\", 