BrideLawNYC)July 26, 2024  Prominent US figures and political commentators condemned the act, arguing it disrespected Christianity and sent a message of exclusion to the 2.4 billion Christians worldwide.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989450302828167, \"rank\": 0.0010497934251078231, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9994693325292319, \"rank\": 0.00053094922814969, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.993945908489084, \"rank\": 0.004830091466695333, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US radio host Clint Russell stated, \\\"Opening your event by replacing Jesus and the disciples with men in drag is unacceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989450302828167, \"rank\": 0.0010497934251078231, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.960044328375291e-18, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999991588132516, \"rank\": 8.411872648563802e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The transnational Left have contempt for Western civilization,\\\" said Tom Fitton, the president of US-based NGO Judicial Watch.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2036, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Fitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Fitton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Fitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Fitton\"}, {\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Non-governmental_organization\", \"score\": 0.9999999949463927, \"rank\": 5.053774914445504e-09, \"text\": \"NGO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Non-governmental_organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Non-governmental_organization\"}, {\"begin\": 2078, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judicial_Watch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Judicial Watch\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judicial_Watch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judicial_Watch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is crazy.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opening your event by replacing Jesus and the disciples at the The Last Supper with men in drag.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999991588132516, \"rank\": 8.411872648563802e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 2.4 billion Christians on earth and apparently the Olympics wanted to declare loudly to all of them, right out of the gateNOT WELCOMEpic.twitter.com/T88AmXbqXL- Clint Russell (@LibertyLockPod)July 26, 2024  AN ABOMINATIONThe opening ceremony of the Olympics mocked Jesus by recreating \\\"The Last Supper' with drag queens, a gay Smurf, and a few children sprinkled in there just for fun.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.993945908489084, \"rank\": 0.004830091466695333, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.960044328375291e-18, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999991588132516, \"rank\": 8.411872648563802e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly overt pagan, satanic symbolism.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"score\": 0.9999999759975257, \"rank\": 2.4002408786926715e-08, \"text\": \"pagan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paganism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they call us conspiracy theorists.pic.twitter.com/ZDHERLl9od  - VINCENT OSHANA (@VincentOshana)July 26, 2024  In their defence, Paris Olympic organisers claimed the show aimed to humorously underline the absurdity of violence among humans.\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2777, \"end\": 2782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0597647825826951e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the backlash continued, with some commentators expressing concerns about the broader implications of mocking religious traditions in a public forum like the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony also included other controversial moments, such as a depiction of a \\\"headless\\\" Marie Antoinette and a scene suggesting a sexual encounter at France's national library,FOX Newsreported.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.496076957106163e-30, \"text\": \"Marie Antoinette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}, {\"begin\": 3219, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9946327961446145, \"rank\": 0.005337674817250097, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swipe Left For Next Video  To all the Christians of the world who are watching the#Paris2024ceremony and felt insulted by this drag queen parody of the Last Supper, know that it is not France that is speaking but a left-wing minority ready for any provocation.#notinmyname\\u00c0 tous les chr\\u00e9tiens du monde\\u2026pic.twitter.com/GusP2TR63u  - Marion Mar\\u00e9chal (@MarionMarechal)July 26, 2024  Conservative French politician and European parliament member Marion Marechal, warned international viewers that this polarising display does not entirely represent French people.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.993945908489084, \"rank\": 0.004830091466695333, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3449, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9946327961446145, \"rank\": 0.005337674817250097, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.996838296237002, \"rank\": 0.003168867246589944, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3679, \"end\": 3705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_European_Parliament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European parliament member\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_European_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_European_Parliament\"}, {\"begin\": 3809, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour